===Noun===
''tricolour''

#A [[flag]] with three stripes either [[vertical]] or [[horizontal]] all of equal size, and of a different colour. This style of flag is used commonly in europe as the national flags of over twenty [[countries]] including [[Belgium]], [[France]], [[Italy]], [[Russia]], [[The Netherlands]] and [[The Republic of Ireland]]

